all of the uiua scripts fallow this convention
the uiua scripts take in a stream from stdin
the arguments are passed as [kes] [values]

example:
uiua script.ua key=val
if the lengths do not match, it will throw an error
if the helps exist, it will return the help string  
the code for this will be in the tools.ua file
in the uiua script this will make a map 
